{"tid":169273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子疑財困 劏房燒炭亡","createTime":"2017-03-24T06:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T07:35:42.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"345dd46dd732f39f589cc59684c32a725e915695","tid":169273,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"男子疑財困 劏房燒炭亡 <br />\n  <br />\n最後更新: 0324 11:12 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0324 10:14 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港仔鴨脷洲山明街16-24號新明大廈，今早9時許，51歲姓吳男子，向58歲胞姐發出Whatapps表示要尋死，其姐立即登門查看，發現事主在單位內燒炭，陷入昏迷，救護員接報到場，將吳送院搶救，惜終告不治。警方調查後，相信死者獨居上址劏房單位，受金錢問題困擾而尋死。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"3c378a9ce3ee8c489baadebe700425a182b580b7","tid":169273,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"387b0b7993654d3c4710d4b781f9b2504d27ee1e","tid":169273,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"住劏房做乜唔申請香港2寶：老綜+公屋？"},{"pid":"5205defe33b5697c0c99da8c519cdae6829d6b57","tid":169273,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住劏房做乜唔申請香港2寶：老綜+公屋？</blockquote><br />\n唔係大陸人"},{"pid":"5011e0a2aceba1d939997f0449dabe4797fc80de","tid":169273,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重擊業主"},{"pid":"ae254b380882651df199fd754fad4ef7c86f28f5","tid":169273,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f55b8feb042d225e6cb513fc3f5d26eb4b1f61b8","tid":169273,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/fa